'''陸潛'''（[[比斯拉马语|比斯拉马语]]：'''Nanggol'''）是[[瓦努阿图|瓦努阿图]][[彭特科斯特岛|彭特科斯特岛]]南部的一种仪式，<ref name="Harewood 2009 94">{{harvnb| Harewood|2009|p = 94}}</ref>是[[高空彈跳|高空彈跳]]的起源。人们从20至30米高的跳台上跳下，仅仅依靠包裹在膝盖上的两根树藤拉住。<ref name="hsw">{{Cite web|url = http://adventure.howstuffworks.com/land-diving.htm|title = How Land Diving Works|author = Debra Ronca|publisher = HowStuffWorks|accessdate = 26 May 2010|archive-date = 2011-07-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110708162842/http://adventure.howstuffworks.com/land-diving.htm|dead-url = no}}</ref>陸潛除了树藤没有任何安全装置。<ref name="abc">{{Cite web|url = http://abcnews.go.com/WNT/story?id=130132&page=1|title = Land Divers of Vanuatu|author = Mike Lee|publisher = ABC News Internet Ventures|accessdate = 24 May 2010|archive-date = 2020-11-27|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201127231304/https://abcnews.go.com/WNT/story?id=130132&page=1|dead-url = no}}</ref>这项传统已经发展为一项旅游特色。<ref name="abc"/><ref>{{harvnb| Jolly| 1994|p = 132}}</ref>根据[[吉尼斯世界纪录|吉尼斯世界纪录]]，在非工业社会的人类体验的最好的感觉就是高空彈跳中落至最低点时的快感。<ref name="MacClancy 1998 xviii">{{harvnb|MacClancy|1998|p = xviii}}</ref>

